M_iFilterType.hint:
Type of morphological filter:<BR>&nbsp;
          0: erosion<BR>&nbsp;
          1: dilation<BR>&nbsp;
          2: Opening<BR>&nbsp;
          3: Closing

Type of morphological filter:<BR>&nbsp;
          0: median<BR>&nbsp;
          1: Gauss<BR>&nbsp;
          2: erosion<BR>&nbsp;
          3: dilation<BR>&nbsp;
          4: Opening<BR>&nbsp;
          5: Closing<BR>&nbsp;
          6: HighPass<BR>&nbsp;
          7: Sharpen<BR>&nbsp;
          8: Histogramm Streching

